1
01:04:10,130 --> 01:04:10,550
Shagal!!!!!

2
01:04:11,250 --> 01:04:11,970
Shagal!!!!

3
01:04:12,950 --> 01:04:14,330
You scratched my car!!!!

4
01:04:15,090 --> 01:04:16,210
When, when?

5
01:04:16,950 --> 01:04:17,390
When?

6
01:04:17,390 --> 01:04:18,730
It wasn't that long ago.

7
01:04:18,770 --> 01:04:19,630
Oh, seriously.

8
01:04:19,950 --> 01:04:20,390
I wasn't swearing or anything.

9
01:04:21,250 --> 01:04:23,010
I told him to pull over because he scratched my car.

10
01:04:25,370 --> 01:04:25,890
Because he kept going.

11
01:04:26,150 --> 01:04:27,030
I needed to see how bad the damage on my car was.

12
01:04:27,030 --> 01:04:29,530
And in that moment I was so startled, I could only say it like that.

13
01:04:29,750 --> 01:04:31,130
I thought he hit me and was running away.

14
01:04:31,790 --> 01:04:33,510
If it felt like a hit-and-run, that makes sense.

15
01:04:33,770 --> 01:04:33,870
Right.

16
01:04:35,510 --> 01:04:35,910
So then...

17
01:04:36,110 --> 01:04:37,230
But why is everyone laughing so much?

18
01:04:37,850 --> 01:04:38,750
Because of 'Shagal.'

19
01:04:39,770 --> 01:04:40,670
So, anyway, anyway, anyway.
